style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;我是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=0cfac9ab584f49059710e82137dd14ba&amp;amp;_e=vwxmWCf2iWKw3c_ayVbeROJq7I9LqoMFzB8iMbo6LQ3NYDjP8M013e0pXTxdnb1ZUtp0qSaNI2O-MPq_09U98eVjSwb2JCJYu6pqMwELhCDrxFc3IxRRIbS1xKvOrcPr8BAKdwMXJr_ZgMPnlDsa56_NRTMJNv5yzC8LlxFpCv88NUH5qUrNyCjeRoMgXiC-u9VyWqEG4xUeh6rDazrJFuHvxgkJrzRqMtugkTIeZ-GHGhPDdr_wRZKz5c-tjwzZewYQ33xNVn6KBh6GKo1C45y7Vafu1sQ0FcUrVlbwF-CTRKnU_iChST6JwfU_G-gWtx0Pud-hkz-zFvtuzNQPMw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;克里斯·安斯蒂&lt;/a&gt;，波士顿的一名经济编辑。今天，我们将关注彭博经济研究对全球基准利率的新展望。将反馈和提示发送至&lt;a href="mailto:ecodaily@bloomberg.net"&gt;ecodaily@bloomberg.net&lt;/a&gt;或通过&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=0cfac9ab584f49059710e82137dd14ba&amp;amp;_e=vwxmWCf2iWKw3c_ayVbeRI1zRbge7-6ciKFNEyutxXsnXrbj2_UEFCjlRBu4dRjG8PKXdFcWnoD5OxIoN__goADNBCYhA5zIJ_QSrhRqDzSAjI_6iUsaJye5OJ6g5I8OcJ6g7gLROnt8OU-GNy2na2CiOh-GZLBxinYOr6kyuzN4YkEHCVBzQce7yZN5CBSf7LsQfv1K10MvfN8T5lSiBvRZosbzfDHsUFYPee9pkU_oOOhDc8O9CksTcc3jw1PvSYGaLu5uV4fU09oMZK5UctaJ1nFh4GnAyZYvqX7FIHTX40sDMS81MzCvL9DlJ0ZlOIzEL3aZjJEmA0RFp9OTf7bETq0P2SNQX4W1tLjHYaQ%3D" target="_blank"&gt;@economics&lt;/a&gt;与 X 取得联系。如果您尚未注册接收本新闻通讯，您可以&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=0cfac9ab584f49059710e82137dd14ba&amp;amp;_e=vwxmWCf2iWKw3c_ayVbeRMdv0N4zElKmwjAHOT9eHy9V-Z0u3_xdQLoB9On2NxauiyYpFVz-OQ6Sh6t5hmbMfwDGNr_