 英里， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=4c23fa335e664d88baabdac0884058fe&amp;amp;_e=MBvWt8YAJ6ZdpH9XInaGMqd3a87Hg6Bp6efDWdfS7y_YfOH5MM7MfeBMYGgz5Iv46PbqNMBql1ug-wlK0ZUIleVJb-lqwi2kU-UKXRJKjRve-uTjZwbWgPemziS-2cZNTTmU3qTSw2OhniwszPhBBjDju3iBs1prwDIU8RLubAk2q-cWIxqGq2KddqA0rPEjpYuYmJT_WJS2MHWpgPFk1d1GiBao8Yedq40xsDVI41Z1Lw08GeDFnZQ14bfEWNGhxLvXsz8B1JI1HoNa0qEl8ZlHdOSy0Gb1Mw2cpLsl5r36QepvsbJLA9ofxmHCZ4jLrxbcPFa7OjlTXoaoOdoZ1g%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;让数百万人感到紧张&lt;/a&gt;。州长加文·纽瑟姆提出了一项&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=4c23fa335e664d88baabdac0884058fe&amp;amp;_e=MBvWt8YAJ6ZdpH9XInaGMg1IBw6pKXl2j0TUyR015biXa9JY0Wlf4r7GH_eg_MRVPReeE2LLj75_-jL2qT5HqezmsT8MeyMmUljRQy4mT4gCLg1FIfAOBdNR4KI6MRV6Mn1YzTJXSH25bTvfvLi6q2HAdDWxsIzzaG8KeioDvXkg9Hb_LzGcjEx8O2p4jNL2cZg3ZMaXqW7AQ_hWTdGOF_b7AWMf7jTKGtdZSmq5JMPPDWWSlbEJxucgBpUYxEaNhGuU3kyo5QsO1Aocj2_1AEDLvvrQnkN2skYZ4Bv1KvyqTT8TN1E8DHPgGp1I1oVB_R6nqe0adj3dsOrhL9qmOA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;25 亿美元的“马歇尔计划”&lt;/a&gt; ，以协助应急响应和恢复工作，因为山火可能导致保险业&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=4c23fa335e664d88baabdac0884058fe&amp;amp;_e=MBvWt8YAJ6ZdpH9XInaGMq-ObUyMcb9w3QWTqpqZxWF-SUZefziUB4J7GOgCaPN1_OWL1PBw74hvAT7FDezNgXG9NPWKOcu8HWxdyD17IqhpnlVZg1u7bTca_mr_s_AtwBtA7P4EDtgU4LNDMfolK56fYn-i9eRPHSjf2e08mm9_pCmSyQOSDpQD50QtGYJAQLyAgTAQfw98bEAaMUWlm6MS39NgEDe06xMail-AJ9cPLrZw-bTSZ6NBURhQBaioNf-aWnpo-ZJHdUcfN7Whh67MEj5CHM2sYFbDzj6Rji8L01uy7jIa4BC3ja8kw4XHxwJUBWvHPbtPh-J_uwi8zg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;损失高达 300 亿美元&lt;/a&gt;。据《华尔街日报》报道，唐纳德·特朗普最早将于下周访问该地区。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特别检察官向司法部提交的一份报告&lt;/strong&gt;得出的结论是，特朗普&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=4c23fa335e664d88baabdac0884058fe&amp;amp;_e=MBvWt8YAJ6ZdpH9XInaGMk-ZDYY5_pAS_d_pX5IfBhoUSdTAhIiPQIoZQjFBHgTW8Y_9Xoa4WVEwomRUonIyIp8xoKomeheIWjydmct073fClIWOdwVAiBbdUsX06QxGbQDCdbH8OZght96bY0jhmazVHR4eyNhJzfRI1nB5Y1gelOgZVWaL96e7UYbWq7YeawCHeFWmkgEoiQUpWuip3QswTzKDcuLR69zkn64yk6SSYI_OKyfcuZy8MlUxRZ6EW_tjiomMdiGkf4h5os9pOy0gg_TKZHoMmzcOjvhHgL_IN0Q2kj-gsbJtgWoKJQzy4_s779BRu8YiS4yiYi2Cgw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;将因试图推翻 2020 年总统选举而被定罪&lt;/a&gt;。这位候任总统反驳说，他“完全无辜”，并抨击特别检察官杰克·史密斯是“笨脑检察官”。更积极的一面是，距离就职日仅剩一周，乌克兰的欧洲盟友对&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=4c23fa335e664d88baabdac0884058fe&amp;amp;_e=MBvWt8YAJ6ZdpH9XInaGMpWCZa_TE6odV6mPQKDB4vD2Cvxdj4PUgkjMddod4_uL9lcxjG4vbEnE6n3_-XkxuheGIBKynZtxzBlNhVSFJfWLQdwtZV-tae_nvBfYi6f2YU-O-3JfQNqIn_E315sjMBbp4xgypNfG505lBmzyktaCJFf_M0LH16I0JFHyXOc9ByR_En8SlIv9PhruRBnM7D3rq1wn6-ey6nuM7jl_ABZFvYdedgMukX1qzr-Mgg0zKsUui-GB1DDogAM4A-3iXQEF1WgNkZspd-saZ6BvRt7ydqU86Dhx1lZPLS3yKjMMd8VnARxqlBwEgbHFVgz2ng%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;特朗普不会迫使基辅&lt;/a&gt;过早与俄罗斯进行谈判持谨慎乐观态度，格陵兰岛则表示&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=4c23fa335e664d88baabdac0884058fe&amp;amp;_e=MBvWt8YAJ6ZdpH9XInaGMvL_T0qRuwVcSH6V0DjUDESmsioWwEB7DJNWKSwqsknkOlJNe8fLGPKItOm2hr1XXPsftE338g9uarErvqUnnZQUXzQsPcItXwnByF2Brthf53-GAGMnSQj5velUhqnbuEZTKKlyCyFcwQX-FAHHG56PSkgs19E7OqoPYkWckEUZYcJFR7hosfVuYUzAwBBMTmZ5m_kq0djfhzjbc6zIaq0zyATx3SdFxeUFx4a2h8duXAjswyTw-lBJzQbRb4gIv9WHZKYBCdZlGz6zGndkVcqHRjRO8rwUKe4Js3uyqwA9_pC8G_7kLpyFJU4sg5dCbA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;愿意与美国建立更密切的关系&lt;/a&gt;。敬请关注。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;加密减速带。&lt;/strong&gt;自 2025 年初以来，比特币的价值已下跌近 5%。加密货币&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=4c23fa335e664d88baabdac0884058fe&amp;amp;_e=MBvWt8YAJ6ZdpH9XInaGMrEjoVyStGQzzl7yPC2vc8Peh5HOC5zBzjBc7p5vBN1A_1Q328lfmp2qwrMsEX5Cv47ahpo7efZchyUbkjq0qTPmOm5Wh9R0w1KngOkHqIxYwjse1FvKt3YY1iIn_89YzTwbAc9u-76Jwdl-ZhYynC4GfnCWyPyXu5FBfGNrFoYM8UO4YPHWaQ9LvSDSgKzm_Q8gn1BMkft_D_xYEoRJL_jUKWPkr3aS-UcDX3Rv-ilnfE3qV4qVdEfP24Nra5CVqFghjuALMWjf-uxniooexReSOzVl8IZgAv5mVqtIdjWAu9dT1ZTFj4Wf7QTqDURxyg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;市场因猜测美联储进一步降息的窗口即将关闭而受到损害&lt;/a&gt;，导致国债收益率上升和美元走强。尽管如此，许多人仍然对&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=4c23fa335e664d88baabdac0884058fe&amp;amp;_e=MBvWt8YAJ6ZdpH9XInaGMvKLl40RnDpnKCmmrEm0HgHJUvgV-5BykIhgbFyMCSRWU_WzorXgHvKyX-vB8Xou2ThPJuZLd3gG8tKf2oncH6-6WXVSMx2IrvQ125IiHuflqaMrAnpJbhMUo0enqepWOd2_IAFy0MV-7o7TIqOqC0OCxskddCbK_ldLQqoQ64nMwj2yUeHELWsB2xm5iOru85UklnFDR7PyIBdCWgMdnEJHnY6PbYsQtVzfxp6zFJZmCOoEv1CKofU3K385jApWeuShIQWFFQx3P3kasyKxssshUFE5mRgSr0wdlji9je9m6v_9GKEPdKKFZEbNpk5sLg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;特朗普领导下的持久繁荣持乐观态度。&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" style="padding: 0 0px;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=4c23fa335e664d88baabdac0884058fe&amp;amp;_e=MBvWt8YAJ6ZdpH9XInaGMuE9EJQ3TA_2yWaQO3PcrJeMnB9tQHOevgKugFvGrAWtgDq1XMVi0vfnRNClpaOTmvjqKxdfH9xQFGORgZC0z4I-FlfzkxqQhDBfiSPFpqOTeag9X1fTnPNEmLTHTEZPwHy-ZA7QPwMbrg5bwEfvKTM6KbjKbYeca6lxiRibdJ6fK8SZNrKysDFqwoT-q9WyQGGd3p3n1DH45srXbS8XLnQo1kFX1dfKYZklU-mQuQVosskJ5FX72ksi1N-QKfbJ1EEhLOqabSbk1Mr9sPWSMONJvLGxgf7k7eTHTt8RhU7aAlJ4P21MkzRQQf5uUHNZYw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="lihide" src="https://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=1099764&amp;amp;stpe=default&amp;amp;li_coord=desktop&amp;amp;collapse_width=550&amp;amp;li=12299371&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=01142025" style="display: block; height: auto; width: 