·格里洛/彭博社&lt;/em&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;圣安娜风本周初将卷土重来，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;洛杉矶将&lt;/strong&gt;面临更多山火， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=ff49d6ed459546dea54f485ddd1967de&amp;amp;_e=7JTVORUV06v3yhvXq5ck5gYFBKBYIW8Fpz7cMUTju0pIomYkONRsPt127wGc11QoVgJ8HVWUib1Tw6TpkD25saon1mUV7UDpBijvKODQLC1TuVoFKWn8wbHBpEoyDW2bdHVpwQYuaj9MQMMB6C3XwHuf6fTMHcv55ABXjSi56Om1JNgC9qxwTA2xXbb14gNBp032RUR79oDeW8QbAV3GJvSPx-0-UntYkqutgBSg6kkDYJ-KRvAtHGrabG6VHZLs5YElsOrUhaAHrvM3A0FNsYgexO4oadEjnDQx2SEDTKaSfNvkQoq0quIlyawKZloCcXrZZCSTMKDuzMgFJpcOtw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;火势可能会进一步加剧，&lt;/a&gt;目前已造成 24 人死亡，12,000 多座建筑物被毁。随着大火肆虐，数百万居民处于危险之中并&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=ff49d6ed459546dea54f485ddd1967de&amp;amp;_e=7JTVORUV06v3yhvXq5ck5hAbqHG3GEmsEk0HelkSyhMbH79edHeIHy6DWCRDJlzmGWcAWevkO28GeV261DOly-OoMi_hZE7LDVYxLtF4P4cPLGOzbRKFZX_2CExyqMThwOw71VjvrMufvGhL1mYC_qYXGhubu8yaMm5BKRLqtj-8-kGCgYNreUDFAa2tO5HobSVjRYHYlUGxhajaPtmOQvzsAjP6szvkRTmKvYj8IEND9xyoF6a4zGQESEvT-0T8JgXiFBLkyOC3TTQZ-DOOFXn9-0pzkBqjViT0BzWzEJXkRKBVCMlx8eGxz2BEE903Rrp_U6ZpyGP8QdyjGO4Dbw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;准备撤离&lt;/a&gt;，AccuWeather &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=ff49d6ed459546dea54f485ddd1967de&amp;amp;_e=7JTVORUV06v3yhvXq5ck5jI2mThr_RcHafVj9lrc1NcdK_Lyn0Q9enknQZYw-h-9-0a5UAWq5L-FTv3_C0XzzhSQoy9f7WydNhBtf-2zAzahghBNUJyhx_P7FaO6fT-n0noBciknwtt9jyKnPqQWDpNtfb00-aUxjTOYQZili6iW5QehvHgEKRwWyCaYUvcsU_qKrGm4iWZL2bvSh58dGi5A0vPURjJXQRBLZnjaFllFDcycoLpkiF-X0z44rszE5cg3CQT6a9LV33-ElDlXeqO2NRkEnSbDJMuaVzKvmjIFY-PkFPpLrx3MAINHyDYuQbSOiyU9BP0ZhdkvhRNJlA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;将损失和经济损失估计提高&lt;/a&gt;至高达 2,750 亿美元。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d