l, sans-serif;"&gt;中国的贸易顺差&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=ff49d6ed459546dea54f485ddd1967de&amp;amp;_e=7JTVORUV06v3yhvXq5ck5hAEAVDEZf-lCZxJEWa6-vDYvdAd2vudAh3LjgrDvgPaWwaJS5x9NyppTfRuUx5QpbDl_sVDTYzez6y7i01Zd_7So53HPbIg-7geeZZXKaueNmSsewPt3YaoV08NvElZUfMn5z4igmEJsQY1E3fC8DsXKMkx2rg3qvnKPvbJySDct4lj3cR-Cqwwh5eVUUX8S-iJKEg84nGffsrjrT57rkK_QJisNUQveUtQ_bPgfh9ezPEY2P_rPAiZvebzJfQTNBrvjxwdjBuoRWfD4u-W8GxoQ3nOUCq6XLAzJri3q4kbMCzaw0Ye2yNwODeSkkFUzw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;飙升至创纪录的9920亿美元&lt;/a&gt;。与此同时，高盛策略师仍&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=ff49d6ed459546dea54f485ddd1967de&amp;amp;_e=7JTVORUV06v3yhvXq5ck5q6zPA3IZDwQ3iPwBkaDUEqPeHY6A50cCtnGn8gifdobYIRMxa3eV_IXlQtDp6cT1Q3y627h07nlXkF87R1qJtRl7SRkV4KhdloCIZOAGCrDaA7uBWg1Cb0HRT79C6eSZIIDow9TtYeTXY1QOnR48H1vcCF_cAr9J80gda4rU73SEvCJtcg5TFwzNTqeb07GltZyQ0LkKz9bDXtgzp9UyR30GuarE0On7-TdSMbuTMowPX7Vj9Mrm33QBtSKmFO0HUw80hYPGAGYtkEFy3aIaUcfaEwPUoCGqmD2iUWOnpXtn1ewF0LNkLCPRLxHsPe0dw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;坚持看好中国股市，&lt;/a&gt;预计基准指数到年底将上涨约20%。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;公司新闻：&lt;/strong&gt;强生公司&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=ff49d6ed459546dea54f485ddd1967de&amp;amp;_e=7JTVORUV06v3yhvXq5ck5ui_8P7-JhZ2kULbhg6WUyMcpkzFftNMynN0PWYAllyVKopBZSXlnuAhJo33j3s7bHvYhRlYWt8_nCvKzQnlfO7kL00gxAANDPNTELrRvOyGyOPWi3JOYSd-9Qkb1ZIWhOdwYeJwTf0jMHEGJYKHQkAs3cgnm1lrfMBc56iPDqHGDAXljXavWhYPFw5u60cng8njUhrXYrnzM-hrZegTUgL4_UayTTh9couRR0IuzhP5mrH7rh0lbp_4xX3QF6LatJUqNzbIwQ_n-5meJonzbImLE7onmYMEID85LlT27xCnptjqYPK1iNNjRSek4I91Ww%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;同意以 146 亿美元收购 Intra-Cellular Therapies，&lt;/a&gt;该公司专注于精神健康障碍和神经系统疾病的新疗法。据《华尔街日报》报道，在高端金融领域，史蒂夫·科恩的 Point72 资产管理公司在公布巨额利润后， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/clic