86rNjwi1UsZNjK1hEAGXSlYaqOFOPt3WtkZTpzu6ZsvwLBv2R8tOlGJGDjyLhNJlFcfQ56nxeDtL3SU3pUHyNezUkNn2CVj940HMLbypIlvbwpq8FKCJoEtNJrX3gFgTR5Jbuxw3xxhkE23H20Lvf_RWmPlOnRjVfVjjKV46tZ6_h_VDVAxV_yX0AaRyERSy6sFAGHXwe-J5AJCBaYXT00OtOnnvMqLcutQe0a8kCSeLjWm0tAScDVJmjfVbNhZwlFjlBl4MCelP-pBBblTWM4HSjy2gW1z_kBbkjTiY1cG3w-d_jkE%3D" target="_blank" title="点击查看网页。"&gt;特别危险的情况&lt;/a&gt;”警告，这是最严重的警报。美国风暴预测中心在一份报告中&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=307da186807b477a8170c737d381c37a&amp;amp;_e=xloyQb76a-ay65Wc1yWUAralJC9X8nO7xyKyV3XP2x_f4dDipOVTMsKZEBHTyGRDyM5HWNyroTXmUoK60maP_tEXrRw77IXFdIjCGqWiNdK9Kcyl76QzYhUFN5mVzCiOjJqU3e8sA5YUL8wi2_gGqsi58UjhaFKrJUk43hFk3WvqswfuG5m2TfBvj5eMr5zZbfMKK6tECVmB7NXwyvtElPClHxRSbBWvyP1v7LBwunbLA8GZ_ozs-gwrETJR4_mfQSS9yqTdj_xCz6FKoWKqI_jeVOEB48XFWSPre5VITV3cVSh4DqjXj0faSWQ6Q3b8Bakz-dyrfyKJx-bulBO4pCrqS98bybpIwTb0VG56oTWJpUnLPR4W0EnmCQe3BgRm4YGa45vS_-lnBxTKlkrNXMuoXrUYPT87EH78GSsAY1Y%3D" target="_blank" title="网站"&gt;称&lt;/a&gt;，近 930 万人面临严重的火灾天气状况。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;根据美国气象局发布的一份咨询报告，虽然即将到来的圣安娜风预计不会像上周席卷洛杉矶的风暴那么强烈，但受到警告的地区“将有很高的风险发生大火， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=307da186807b477a8170c737d381c37a&amp;amp;_e=xloyQb76a-ay65Wc1yWUAgmpa5erBn6QBzCV1ZikGeflfsqFdVAaNuU0qQJvNFAhfVv3rbVOeqgeSyHk1pdmv_4IjEP5qhRdyc5Z4LF8AuNwMZNRECX0-r--z9GSaXy0gAsF-3-CnPK0U2O6uCb3is_Bjfge1WW799Le7oqteteSf7A7W8Abeja9LW-PrytldKCB9mUZ5SW4qUaLMTfp9gFQ5yjSSzk6Z2qj6z6UUdQ1WELpJzxh688KXl0o5ZRwslgVXLO4EOQcK3Di8cH-pjNIfGDUKJHv6u5LymKJznnJTEoZT2MqbgbhO6819e2RI9tvu5Z1zuf1b0sMjTW9pGiYRIi5J6Xiu56nTdIMWqYUVQHfJic20HN7HOn2hzA4KxmnEqDpcSr82By4W0VWIbN4nRmPY4UjySrG7T5bNAU%3D" target="_blank" title="国家气象局咨询"&gt;火势蔓延非常迅速&lt;/a&gt;”。国家气象局周日晚间。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;大风将限制消防员在扑灭快速蔓延的 Palisades 和 Eaton 大火方面取得进展的机会，这场大火已造成洛杉矶 Pacific Palisades 和 Altadena 社区至少&lt;a href="https:/